name: M_INT_TO_STRING
value:
do \
    { \
        char rev[5 * sizeof(int) / 2]; \
        int i = 0, digits = 0; \
        if ((signed_v) && (val) < 0) \
        { \
            buffer[i] = '-'; \
            i++; \
        } \
        do \
        { \
            rev[digits++] = '0' + abs((val) % 10); \
            (val) /= 10; \
        } \
        while ((val) != 0); \
        for (; digits > 0 && i < (buffer_len); i++) \
            buffer[i] = rev[--digits]; \
        buffer[i] = 0; \
        (buffer_len) = i; \
    } while (0)
